    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 17.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第17课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Always Young.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "永远年轻。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question, Why doesn't Aunt Jennifer tell anyone how old she is?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题：为什么詹妮弗姑妈从不告诉别人她的年龄？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "My Aunt Jennifer is an actress.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我的姑妈詹妮弗是一名演员。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "She must be at least 35 years old.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她至少也有35岁了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "In spite of this, she often appears on the stage as a young girl.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "尽管如此，她却常在舞台上扮演年轻姑娘。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "Jennifer will have to take part in a new play soon.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "詹妮弗很快又要参加一出新剧的演出。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "This time, she will be a girl of 17.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这一次，她将扮演一个17岁的少女。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "In the play, she must appear in a bright red dress and long black stockings.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "剧中她必须穿一条鲜红色连衣裙和黑色长筒袜。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Last year, in another play, she had to wear short socks and a bright orange colored dress.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "去年，在另一出戏里，她得穿短袜和一条鲜橙色的连衣裙。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "If anyone ever asks her how old she is, she always answers, Darling, it must be terrible to be grown up.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "要是有人问她多大年纪，她总是回答：“亲爱的，长大成人一定很可怕吧！”"
      }
    }
  ],
